&lt;h2 id=&#34;Vim-Docker&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://hub.docker.com/r/bloodstar/vim&#34;&gt;Vim Docker&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://i.imgur.com/G6KybVM.png&#34; alt=&#34;Vim Docker&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;code-area&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;line-numbers language-bash&#34; data-language=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34;&gt;docker pull bloodstar/vim&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;code-area&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;line-numbers language-bash&#34; data-language=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34;&gt;alias edit=&#39;docker run -ti --rm -v $(pwd):/home/developer/workspace bloodstar/vim&#39; 
